The feature reduction module consists of three different CNNs, one for each input channel, leading to a latent low dimensionality representation consisting of 100 latent features for each channel. The sMRI channel was analyzed through a 3D CNN (sMRI-CNN) defined by six convolutional layers (filter sizes of \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
