Figure 2A
).

Feces: All samples in HG, COG and COPG group contained 49126 ASVs: 116 ASVs in HG and COG group; 88 ASVs in HG and COPG group; 161 ASVs in COG and COPG group; ASVs 1753 unique to HG group; ASVs 2926 unique to COG group; ASVs 2372 unique to COPG group (
Figure 2B
).

